title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show DEC-12-2013 THURS
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show DEC-12-2013 THURS







The Glenn Beck Program




Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET




        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 12/12/13Thursday, December 12, 2013 10:49 AM




Information has come out that the sign language interpreter at Nelson Mandela's funeral,

      who stood just feet away from the president, 
        turned out to, not only, not know sign language at all, 
          but be a self confessed schizophrenic with violent tendencies.

   Glenn and the guys discuss how it's possible that this guy was able
      to get so close to the president. 

 Also, the scary way that the White House is silencing the press. 

      Plus, Glenn wants a TX judge recalled,  and he explains the unforgivable reason why.
